NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
A.D., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
S.R. and J.M., Defendants. In the Matter of A.D.-R. and N.R., Minors-Respondents. C-305 September Term 2017
079264 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 14, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000642-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
